outputs.output_descr: The project aims to strengthen capacities within the public sector to effectively mainstream HIV and AIDS into planning and budgeting processes of different offices, ministries and agencies. It further supports implementation of workplace programmes across the public sector.

project_descr: The project aims to strengthen capacities of the governance sector as outlined in the NSF to support revised coordination mechanisms of the HIV/AIDS national response and support mainstreaming efforts into development planning processes.
project_title: Strengthening Capacities for Improved HIV Coordination
